Package: ggIRT
Type: Package
Title: Visualize Item Response Category Characteristic Curves, Item Characteristic Curves, Item Information Curves, and Test Information Curve
Version: 1.0.1
Author: Tatsuya IKEDA
Maintainer: Tatsuya IKEDA <ikeda.tatsuya.clpsy@gmail.com>
Description: Visualuze IRCCC, ICC, IIC, and TIC from a mirt object, using the ggplot2 package.
    The scale factor D = 1.701 is often used, but the `ltm` package uses D = 1.00. Therefore, the objects generated by the `ltm` package (`ltm` objects and `grm` objects) are corrected to D = 1.701. Therefore, the shapes of the curves differ between the visualization using the `ltm` package and the visualization using this package.
